             fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"
             filter="url(#icon-sketch)"/>
     </svg>
     \`\`\`

7. **Smooth Animation Effects**
   - Avoid rigid transitions, use elastic easing
   - Recommended easing: cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55)
   - Example:
     \`\`\`css
