     column-count: 2;
     column-gap: 2rem;
     column-rule: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
     text-align: justify;
   }
   \`\`\`

4. **Classic Dividers**:
   - Double-line: border-top: 3px double #000
   - Dotted line: border-bottom: 1px dotted #d1d5db
   - Example:
   \`\`\`css
